comment.shortText:
Get WHOIS-like information for a name, including the address that owns it,
the block at which it expires, and the zone file anchored to it (if available).
comment.text: This is intended for use in third-party wallets or in DApps that register names.

tags.text: the name to query.  Can be on-chain of off-chain.
a promise that resolves to the WHOIS-like information
